data.description:
Your wait is Over! Come see this Beautiful  
4 bedroom 2 1/2 Bath home in Cedarbrook Subdivision  this home has everything you are looking for, Large Master Suite with a separate tub and shower, Gourmet Kitchen, Spacious Family Room and Dining Room. Plus Bonus room/Loft upstairs. Screened Lani with an extended patio and Huge back yard for relaxing or entertaining the Family and large enough for a pool. Close to River City Towncenter with a brand-new Publix less than 1 mile away lots of shopping and great restaurants..
Schedule your showing today!
